        "layout": "concept-full",
        "layoutData": {
          "title": "Five Key Strategies",
          "paragraphs": [
            "Match your deductible to your emergency savings and risk tolerance. Higher deductible = lower premiums.",
            "HSAs offer triple tax advantages: tax-deductible contributions, tax-free growth, and tax-free withdrawals for medical expenses.",
            "Using in-network providers can significantly reduce costsâ€”out-of-network often means higher deductibles and co-insurance.",
            "Get quotes from multiple insurers. Compare all cost components, not just premiums. Bundle policies for discounts."
